caption.title: Phylogenetic analysis of the CprM gene sequences of DENV-1 isolates from the Klang Valley.
caption.p: Sample sequence of DENV-1 (429 nt) from adult Ae. aegypti collected from Selangor in this study (marked with a white triangle) is labelled with the GenBank accession number, sample ID and year of collection. Bootstrap values (1,000 replicates) are shown next to the branches. Taxa of reference sequences are labelled as the GenBank accession numbers, year and country of sample collection.
